AVAILABLE FOR ADOPTION!!! Meet Blaze, a handsome Shepherd/Hound mix born around September 21st 2017. Blaze is a mild mannered puppy with an easy going disposition. He was recently rescued from a local shelter with his sister Petunia. He is currently in a foster home with his sister and adjusting well. Blaze loves to play and romp around with his sister and his fosters other dogs. He is great with everyone he meets, kids, dogs and cats. He is a good boy that is
very treat motived and learning basic commands. He loves attention especially belly rubs! Blaze currently weighs around 20lbs and will weigh around 70lbs full grown. He would love a home with fenced in backyard to run and play in and someone that is home more often than not. He would be best suited in a home with children 5 years old or older. If you are looking for a new addition to your home, contact us today at adopt@carolinapaws.com to meet Blaze. #Carolinapaws, #dog, #dogs, #adopt, #adoption, #rescue, #petfinder, #dogsofinstagram, #sweet, #charlotte, #lovedogs, #rescuedog, #cute, #rescuesrock, #rescuedogsofinstagram, #adorable, #secondchance, #northcarolina, #adoptlove, #loverescues, #saved #Waxhaw #clt #charlottenc #adoptdontshop #704 #puppy

AVAILABLE FOR ADOPTION!!! Meet Petunia, a sweet and lovable Shepherd/Hound mix born around September 21st 2017. Petunia is a typical fun and playful puppy. This beautiful girl is a very social puppy that loves everyone she meets. She was recently rescued from a local shelter with her brother Blaze. She is currently in a foster home with her brother and adjusting well. She loves to run and play in her fosters backyard and wrestling with her brother. She is a very smart girl that is treat motivated. She is already mastering the sit command at her. Petunia currently weighs around 20lbs and will weigh around 70lbs full grown. She would love a home with fenced in backyard to run and play in and someone that is home more often than not. She would be best suited in a home with children 5 years old and older. If you are looking for a new addition to your home, contact us today at adopt@carolinapaws.com to meet Petunia. #Carolinapaws, #dog, #dogs, #adopt, #adoption, #rescue, #petfinder, #dogsofinstagram, #sweet, #charlotte, #lovedogs, #rescuedog, #cute, #rescuesrock, #rescuedogsofinstagram, #adorable, #secondchance, #northcarolina, #adoptlove, #loverescues, #saved #Waxhaw #clt #charlottenc #adoptdontshop #704 #puppy
